<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="firm-adv">firm <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fɜːm/    美 /fɜːrm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>稳固地；坚定地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please stand firm and hold the handrail.
站稳并扶好扶手。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Always <strong>hold firm to</strong> your beliefs.
始终要坚持自己的信仰。</p></div></div>